---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Accessibility Statement"
  description="Golden Pathway is committed to digital accessibility. Read our Accessibility Statement to learn about our standards and compliance."
>
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
      Accessibility Statement
    </h1>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-main leading-relaxed">
        Golden Pathway ("we", "us", or "our") is committed to making our website
        accessible to as many people as possible, in accordance with the Public
        Sector Bodies (Websites and Mobile Applications) (No. 2) Accessibility
        Regulations 2018 and the Equality Act 2010.
      </p>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-text-main">Our Commitment</h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-main leading-relaxed">
        We aim to ensure our website is usable by everyone, regardless of
        ability or technology. We strive to:
      </p>
      <ul
        class="list-disc pl-6 text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-main leading-relaxed"
      >
        <li>Use clear and simple language</li>
        <li>Ensure sufficient colour contrast</li>
        <li>Make navigation consistent and logical</li>
        <li>Support keyboard navigation</li>
        <li>Provide alternative text for images</li>
        <li>Use semantic HTML for structure</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-text-main">
        How Accessible Is This Website?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-main leading-relaxed">
        We know some parts of this website may not be fully accessible. We are
        continually working to improve accessibility and welcome your feedback.
      </p>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-text-main">
        Reporting Accessibility Problems
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-main leading-relaxed">
        If you experience any difficulty accessing information on this site, or
        would like to suggest improvements, please contact us:
      </p>
      <ul
        class="list-disc pl-6 text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-main leading-relaxed"
      >
        <li>
          Email: <a href="mailto:info@goldenpathway.co.uk" class="underline"
            >info@goldenpathway.co.uk</a>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-text-main">
        Enforcement Procedure
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-main leading-relaxed">
        If you are not satisfied with our response, you can contact the Equality
        Advisory and Support Service (EASS) for further advice: <a
          href="https://www.equalityadvisoryservice.com/"
          class="underline"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener">www.equalityadvisoryservice.com</a
        >
      </p>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-text-main">
        Preparation of This Statement
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-main leading-relaxed">
        This statement was prepared on 12 November 2025. It will be reviewed and
        updated as necessary.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
